; Tests for commodity.cc: downloaded quote commodity mismatch
; Covers: (quote returned but commodity doesn't match in_terms_of)
; The getquote script returns a GBP-denominated price when $ is expected,
; so the quote is rejected and the old cached price ($1.05) is used instead.

P 2020/01/01 EUR $1.05

2024/01/15 Test
    Expenses  10 EUR
    Assets

test bal -X '$' -Q --getquote $sourcepath/test/scripts/getquote-wrong-commodity.sh -> 0
             $-10.50  Assets
              $10.50  Expenses
--------------------
                   0
end test
